snippet.title: Pragma Arbiter Trailer
snippet.description:
Pragma Arbiter is a match-based multiplayer game with a series of different game modes where you can play as a mage, rogue, or knight. The game modes include Adventure, Casual Team Battle, Ranked 3v3 Team Battle, 1v1 Duel, and Arena.

Visit pragma.gg to learn more!
